WEBVTT

00:22.065 --> 00:23.719
First the fucking UN,

00:23.719 --> 00:25.547
Now they blew up
your goddamn house.

00:25.547 --> 00:27.157
Let me protect you.

00:27.157 --> 00:28.550
I'm already
a dead man walking.

00:28.550 --> 00:30.247
There's nothing you
or anyone can do about it.

00:30.247 --> 00:32.510
There's another shipment,
bigger than the one we had.

00:32.510 --> 00:34.860
You and I, let's handle it.

00:34.860 --> 00:36.340
I gotta save my friend.

00:36.340 --> 00:38.342
My father's gonna come
gunning for you.

00:38.342 --> 00:40.605
This isn't about Harlem.
It's about me.

00:40.605 --> 00:43.173
Look, I'm gonna show him
the utmost respect

00:43.173 --> 00:44.957
at the sit-down tomorrow.

00:45.784 --> 00:48.091
If any of youse have
agreements with Colombo,

00:48.091 --> 00:49.701
they no longer matter.

00:49.701 --> 00:51.355
I want Joe the fuck
out of Harlem.

00:51.355 --> 00:54.097
Jose Battle and I have
a plan to give you--

00:54.097 --> 00:55.925
Havana.
With the help of the CIA,

00:55.925 --> 00:58.101
you can rebuild
your casinos there.

00:58.101 --> 00:59.102
They ain't got fuckin'
no connections to the--

00:59.102 --> 01:00.756
Good evening, gentlemen.

01:00.756 --> 01:03.411
Allow me to explain what
your government can do for you.

01:04.238 --> 01:05.413
The fuck is this?

01:05.413 --> 01:06.544
I just want my daughter.

01:06.544 --> 01:07.937
I'm staying here with Joe.

01:09.765 --> 01:12.072
Hey, Elise.
I'm sorry, d--

01:12.072 --> 01:15.379
Your father thinks
he can blackmail me.

01:15.379 --> 01:17.555
No, no, no.
No, no. Please, don't!

01:17.555 --> 01:19.731
But I can make his life
as miserable...

01:23.996 --> 01:25.824
<i>...as he makes mine.</i>

01:25.824 --> 01:27.913
<i>I reconsidered
your proposal.</i>

01:27.913 --> 01:30.264
Let's take back Harlem.

01:34.529 --> 01:37.401
I won't ever do anything
to threaten you again.

01:37.401 --> 01:39.099
I swear.

01:40.361 --> 01:43.146
What exactly do you have
in terms of documentation?

01:43.146 --> 01:44.930
Thought you might ask.

01:44.930 --> 01:45.888
Here.

01:47.281 --> 01:49.457
It's Operation Mongoose.

01:49.457 --> 01:52.242
Your plan to kill Castro
using mob hitmen.

01:57.247 --> 02:01.686
Look, my daughter
means everything to me.

02:01.686 --> 02:03.601
You obviously know that.

02:03.601 --> 02:06.778
That she's fragile.

02:06.778 --> 02:08.606
That, uh, hotshot
you gave her--

02:08.606 --> 02:10.130
it almost killed her.

02:10.130 --> 02:13.176
I wanted to send a message,
not end her life.

02:13.176 --> 02:15.222
Message received.

02:18.050 --> 02:19.791
Just wanted you
to know that.

02:32.500 --> 02:37.157
The Bay of Pigs
invasion was an embarrassment.

02:37.157 --> 02:40.377
We were left stranded
on the beach,

02:40.377 --> 02:42.684
imprisoned,

02:42.684 --> 02:46.383
abandoned and betrayed
by that fucking coward,

02:46.383 --> 02:50.518
Jack Kennedy,
who had promised us air support.

02:52.215 --> 02:54.913
But that's not gonna
happen again.

02:54.913 --> 02:56.567
Our second invasion
will be successful,

02:56.567 --> 03:00.049
and we will take back Cuba
from Castro.

03:12.061 --> 03:14.716
This is our chance, Vincent.

03:14.716 --> 03:16.326
We can be bigger in Havana

03:16.326 --> 03:18.850
than we ever were
in the glory days.

03:18.850 --> 03:21.592
There's a supply of cocaine,
heroin, and weapons

03:21.592 --> 03:25.030
from the CIA
coming tomorrow.

03:25.030 --> 03:27.511
The guns will be trucked
to Louisiana,

03:27.511 --> 03:29.774
where my militia
is training.

03:29.774 --> 03:32.516
We want to use Randall's Island
for the drop,

03:32.516 --> 03:34.126
your territory.

03:34.126 --> 03:38.696
Now, the other bosses
have already agreed, so...

03:38.696 --> 03:41.221
if you're amenable,

03:41.221 --> 03:44.441
we can move forward
without hesitation.

03:48.140 --> 03:51.231
How much is my cut?

03:51.231 --> 03:54.364
Well, I estimate...

03:54.364 --> 03:56.584
upwards of $10 million.

03:59.804 --> 04:01.415
Yeah.

04:03.330 --> 04:04.418
♪ Hey

04:16.430 --> 04:17.866
How you doing?

04:20.347 --> 04:22.784
Oh, this is good, right?

04:22.784 --> 04:25.787
You and me, making a shitload
of money together.

04:28.137 --> 04:30.400
You think big,
I'll give you that.

04:30.400 --> 04:32.141
Eh, you know,

04:32.141 --> 04:34.012
it was your daughter
that pegged Randall's Island

04:34.012 --> 04:36.972
as the perfect drop spot.

04:36.972 --> 04:39.801
She's been advising me,
you know?

04:39.801 --> 04:41.803
What do you mean,
advising you?

04:41.803 --> 04:44.588
Well, she obviously learned
a lot from you.

04:44.588 --> 04:46.460
Got a real good head
on her shoulders.

04:46.460 --> 04:48.810
Mm.

04:48.810 --> 04:51.378
With a face to match,
you know what I mean?

04:54.381 --> 04:57.427
Yeah.

04:57.427 --> 04:59.124
She does.

04:59.124 --> 05:01.301
I swear to Christ,
it was all I could do

05:01.301 --> 05:03.128
not to snap
that prick's neck.

05:03.128 --> 05:05.609
Well, you gotta keep
cool. Just work that angle.

05:05.609 --> 05:07.829
It's my girl.
It's hard.

05:07.829 --> 05:09.526
Who you talking to?

05:09.526 --> 05:11.615
If it wasn't
for our plan,

05:11.615 --> 05:14.183
Harvey'd be a grease spot
right now.

05:14.183 --> 05:15.967
He bought it?

05:15.967 --> 05:17.317
Fuck if I know.

05:17.317 --> 05:19.144
Gotta be ready
to stick and move.

05:19.144 --> 05:21.364
Or we could just blow all these
motherfuckers' heads off now

05:21.364 --> 05:22.800
and end it.

05:24.541 --> 05:26.195
No rash moves.

05:26.195 --> 05:28.850
But things go well,
this time tomorrow,

05:28.850 --> 05:31.374
we'll be back
in control of Harlem.

05:31.374 --> 05:32.897
Yeah.

05:32.897 --> 05:34.986
Tomorrow's the day.

