My station chief
in West Berlin

18:36.332 --> 18:39.030
used to toss a cat
out a three-story window

18:39.030 --> 18:41.250
so we could all watch

18:41.250 --> 18:43.992
what makes them always land
on their feet.

18:43.992 --> 18:45.428
You know how?

18:45.428 --> 18:47.169
I don't believe I care.

18:47.169 --> 18:49.693
Well, it's
a righting reflex.

18:49.693 --> 18:54.829
No matter how the cat's thrown,
it bends and twists

18:54.829 --> 18:58.354
until its ass is in
the right position to land.

18:58.354 --> 19:00.443
Johnson wasn't
cooperating,

19:00.443 --> 19:04.708
so I bent and twisted
until I found what worked.

19:04.708 --> 19:06.406
That is what I do.

19:08.712 --> 19:11.541
A cat has nine lives.

19:11.541 --> 19:13.630
Even if it breaks its neck,

19:13.630 --> 19:17.199
it can come back
and fuck with you.

19:17.199 --> 19:19.462
Johnson's not stupid.

19:19.462 --> 19:21.464
He knows the power
and the reach of the CIA,

19:21.464 --> 19:25.381
and he's not stupid enough
to fuck with me.

19:25.381 --> 19:27.470
You kidnapped
his daughter.

19:27.470 --> 19:30.908
He sees you as a threat
to Malcolm X.

19:30.908 --> 19:35.783
Johnson has a "righting reflex,"
just like you do.

19:40.135 --> 19:42.006
Fine.

19:42.006 --> 19:45.749
I'll, uh...
have him tailed.

19:45.749 --> 19:49.492
I'll be on his ass
if he tries anything.

19:49.492 --> 19:51.581
Mm. Ugh.

19:51.581 --> 19:53.714
You have to finish
that shit.

19:56.717 --> 19:59.328
I asked you here
for two reasons.

19:59.328 --> 20:01.896
One, I'd like you to meet
Mr. Cyril DeGrasse Tyson.

20:01.896 --> 20:03.680
Oh, it's an honor.

20:03.680 --> 20:05.378
I have admired your work
in education

20:05.378 --> 20:07.684
and urban outreach
for years.

20:07.684 --> 20:09.120
Thank you.

20:09.120 --> 20:13.168
And second,
to give you this.

20:16.519 --> 20:19.914
Well, it's wonderful,
but unnecessary.

20:19.914 --> 20:21.350
You deserve it.

20:21.350 --> 20:23.874
I wanted there to be some
tangible recognition

20:23.874 --> 20:25.398
for all the work
you've done.

20:25.398 --> 20:27.138
Well, the work's
just getting started.

20:27.138 --> 20:29.271
Let me cut
to the chase.

20:29.271 --> 20:31.621
I'm the new administrative
director at HARYOU,

20:31.621 --> 20:33.580
and I'm afraid...

20:33.580 --> 20:35.538
you're out.

20:35.538 --> 20:36.757
Cyril--

20:36.757 --> 20:38.541
There's no room
for gangsters

20:38.541 --> 20:41.065
or their wives
in this organization.

20:41.065 --> 20:42.719
It isn't the message
that I wish to send

20:42.719 --> 20:45.113
to our community
or our children.

20:48.769 --> 20:51.728
Does Congressman Powell
know about this?

20:51.728 --> 20:53.991
It-- It wasn't his choice,
nor mine,

20:53.991 --> 20:56.994
but Cyril has been tasked
by the governor

20:56.994 --> 20:59.910
with merging his community
action program with ours,

20:59.910 --> 21:03.784
so he's calling the shots.

21:03.784 --> 21:05.655
I'm sorry, Mayme.

21:08.441 --> 21:11.748
Well, Mr. Tyson,

21:11.748 --> 21:14.490
I wish you
the best of luck.

21:14.490 --> 21:18.015
And if you don't mind, I'd like
to make one last contribution.

21:18.015 --> 21:19.278
What is it?

21:19.278 --> 21:21.802
It's this.

21:21.802 --> 21:25.806
Why don't you take it
and shove it up your ass?

21:52.876 --> 21:55.531
Joe.

21:55.531 --> 21:57.359
I'm leaving.

21:57.359 --> 21:59.492
I just wanted
to say goodbye.

21:59.492 --> 22:01.320
What?

22:01.320 --> 22:04.627
That ticket to Paris
you gave me-- I'm gonna use it.

22:04.627 --> 22:06.237
The fuck are you
talking about?

22:06.237 --> 22:08.718
I'll send for the rest
of my things later.

22:08.718 --> 22:10.546
What is this?
What happened?

22:10.546 --> 22:13.244
Why can't you call this off
for your own safety?

22:13.244 --> 22:14.811
Call this off?

22:14.811 --> 22:16.900
This is everything
I've been working for.

22:16.900 --> 22:18.902
I don't wanna see
how it ends.

22:18.902 --> 22:22.471
Stella,
this is business.

22:22.471 --> 22:24.386
I know
what the fuck I'm doing.

22:24.386 --> 22:26.345
My father
will crush you.

22:28.608 --> 22:31.480
Everybody,
get the fuck out.

22:31.480 --> 22:33.264
Get the fuck out!

22:39.662 --> 22:44.493
I have this
under control.

22:44.493 --> 22:47.888
This is the biggest fucking deal
of my life,

22:47.888 --> 22:49.672
and you're just gonna
fucking leave?

22:49.672 --> 22:51.152
Yeah.

22:53.284 --> 22:55.243
Go.

22:55.243 --> 22:56.766
Joe.

22:58.333 --> 23:00.553
Before I get
on that plane,

23:00.553 --> 23:03.643
I'm gonna take one last shot
at saving your life.

23:05.645 --> 23:07.342
Wish me luck.

23:14.131 --> 23:15.698
What makes you think
Robert Morgenthau

23:15.698 --> 23:17.439
ain't gonna turn around
and fuck us?

23:17.439 --> 23:20.573
There's enough information
in that Operation Mongoose file

23:20.573 --> 23:23.880
to fry both the FBI
and the CIA.

23:23.880 --> 23:28.319
If Morgenthau can nail Harvey,
it'll grant us immunity.

23:28.319 --> 23:31.105
William Harvey is our
life insurance policy.

23:33.324 --> 23:36.110
Yeah, but insurance
doesn't usually pay off

23:36.110 --> 23:38.242
until after you're dead.

23:44.161 --> 23:45.989
Take your weapons
and toss them to the ground.

23:45.989 --> 23:48.078
Don't make me shoot you
between the eyes.

23:56.565 --> 23:59.089
First off, I don't appreciate
your efforts

23:59.089 --> 24:01.962
to cut a deal
with Robert Morgenthau.

24:01.962 --> 24:04.486
Think I didn't have a plant
in his office?

24:04.486 --> 24:06.009
Morgenthau arrests me,

24:06.009 --> 24:08.751
and in exchange for immunity,
you go scot-free.

24:08.751 --> 24:10.492
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

24:10.492 --> 24:12.320
That's clever.

24:12.320 --> 24:15.497
You ever want to work for
the CIA, I'll find you a job.

24:15.497 --> 24:18.457
- What do you want?
- Gigante, I need you

24:18.457 --> 24:20.589
to secure the delivery
on Randall's Island.

24:20.589 --> 24:22.765
Johnson, I need you
to distribute the narcotics.

24:22.765 --> 24:25.115
Who the fuck
you think you are?

24:25.115 --> 24:30.120
You both have
daughters, right?

24:30.120 --> 24:32.471
You are protective of them.

24:32.471 --> 24:35.517
Do as I ask,
clam up with the Feds,

24:35.517 --> 24:37.606
and we can all be friends.

24:37.606 --> 24:40.304
You're threatening
my daughter?

24:40.304 --> 24:42.959
I'm not your enemy.
I'm your benefactor.

24:42.959 --> 24:45.005
We're all gonna make
a lot of money.

24:45.005 --> 24:46.789
Just do what you're told

24:46.789 --> 24:49.488
and I will never have to think
about your children again.

24:49.488 --> 24:51.141
What about Morgenthau?

24:51.141 --> 24:54.231
Read him a fucking fairy tale
if he wants dirt on me.

24:54.231 --> 24:55.798
I got you covered.

24:55.798 --> 24:57.408
Nobody'll touch you.

24:57.408 --> 24:58.671
You got all the cards.

24:58.671 --> 25:00.977
Well, that's correct.

25:00.977 --> 25:04.154
But I can't fault you
for trying.

25:04.154 --> 25:05.982
Do we have
an agreement?

25:20.823 --> 25:22.651
Agreed.

25:34.794 --> 25:37.405
I think our life insurance
just got canceled.

25:43.585 --> 25:45.544
What's to keep Morgenthau
from arresting us

25:45.544 --> 25:47.676
once he sees
that Harvey's not there?

25:47.676 --> 25:49.591
Not much.

25:51.114 --> 25:53.595
If you want to bail,
I'll go this alone.

25:58.252 --> 26:00.123
Fuck it.

26:00.123 --> 26:04.388
Fuck it, I'd rather be dead than
let Colombo take what's ours.

26:04.388 --> 26:05.912
Mm.

26:16.749 --> 26:18.533
You're home.

26:21.971 --> 26:23.625
I've been fired.

26:23.625 --> 26:25.322
What?

26:28.108 --> 26:31.067
HARYOU has a new director.

26:31.067 --> 26:34.593
Cyril DeGrasse Tyson.

26:34.593 --> 26:38.422
He doesn't want me involved
because I'm married to you.

26:38.422 --> 26:39.815
Congressman Powell
know about this?

26:39.815 --> 26:43.253
He's in Washington.
It was a sneak attack.

26:43.253 --> 26:45.081
Just humiliating.

26:45.081 --> 26:46.256
I'll see what
I can do about it.

26:46.256 --> 26:47.997
Oh, don't bother.

26:50.391 --> 26:54.438
They will never accept me
as long as I am with you.

26:54.438 --> 26:55.962
Mayme, I don't think
that's true.

26:55.962 --> 27:00.793
In your heart,
you are a good man, Ellsworth.

27:04.710 --> 27:07.669
But you and I have
both made immoral choices.

27:07.669 --> 27:09.105
Mayme, please.

27:09.105 --> 27:12.021
You-- You helped keep
that organization alive.

27:12.021 --> 27:15.764
When I married you...

27:15.764 --> 27:17.984
I made a deal
with the devil.

27:21.509 --> 27:23.554
And I just have
to accept that.

27:47.361 --> 27:51.582
Dear Lord Jesus, we beseech you
to bless this family

27:51.582 --> 27:54.150
and to guide us to be better
instruments of thine will.

27:54.150 --> 27:55.761
Amen.

27:58.285 --> 28:00.853
Yeah, well...

28:00.853 --> 28:02.985
I could use a prayer

28:02.985 --> 28:05.466
that helps me
destroy my enemies.

28:07.773 --> 28:09.992
Vincent, we must trust

28:09.992 --> 28:11.559
that the Lord knows
what's best for you.

28:15.128 --> 28:17.173
- Am I interrupting?
- No.

28:17.173 --> 28:18.697
What are you doing here?

28:18.697 --> 28:20.350
I just came
to get some things.

28:20.350 --> 28:22.439
I'm leaving
the country.

28:23.658 --> 28:25.747
What about Colombo?

28:25.747 --> 28:28.184
That was a mistake.

28:28.184 --> 28:29.882
A big one.

28:29.882 --> 28:32.754
Stella, praise the Lord
that you've come to your senses.

28:32.754 --> 28:34.016
Yeah.

28:34.016 --> 28:36.453
Dad...

28:36.453 --> 28:39.848
are you gonna kill
Joe Colombo?

28:39.848 --> 28:42.459
No.
I don't kill people, Stella.

28:42.459 --> 28:44.200
Fuck you.
I need you to promise me

28:44.200 --> 28:45.636
that you're not gonna kill him.

28:45.636 --> 28:47.638
You heard him.
He's not gonna harm anyone.

28:47.638 --> 28:49.858
Uncle Louie, your head's shoved
so far up your fucking Bible,

28:49.858 --> 28:51.425
you won't admit
what's right in front of you.

28:51.425 --> 28:53.427
And you need to admit
your sins to the Lord.

28:53.427 --> 28:54.907
Would you
shut the fuck up?

28:54.907 --> 28:57.126
You can both rot in hell.

28:57.126 --> 28:59.781
I don't even care this time.
I'm going to Paris.

28:59.781 --> 29:02.436
No, stay here, stay here.
Listen to me.

29:05.308 --> 29:08.050
O-Olympia,
she's gone, right?

29:08.050 --> 29:09.617
For good.

29:11.532 --> 29:14.230
And I promise, I-I won't lay
a hand on Colombo.

29:14.230 --> 29:16.319
How can I possibly
trust you?

29:16.319 --> 29:18.408
Well, that's easy.

29:18.408 --> 29:21.107
Joe told me that you gave him
the idea for Randall's Island.

29:21.107 --> 29:22.586
So?

29:22.586 --> 29:24.197
It was smart.

29:26.199 --> 29:27.940
She's a smart girl.

29:29.463 --> 29:32.814
So, you stay here.

29:32.814 --> 29:36.252
You work with me.

29:36.252 --> 29:39.255
I'll bring you
into everything I do,

29:39.255 --> 29:41.562
and I'll give you a piece,
a good piece.

29:44.957 --> 29:47.307
Will that
make you happy?

29:49.831 --> 29:52.791
How strong is the trust
that you set up for my family?

29:52.791 --> 29:56.838
They could live
to the biblical age of 900

29:56.838 --> 29:58.797
and do it in style.

30:02.017 --> 30:04.150
And what if something
happened to me?

30:04.150 --> 30:07.153
What's gonna happen
to you?

30:07.153 --> 30:11.200
- It's a thought experiment.
- Is everything alright?

30:11.200 --> 30:13.507
Just wanna make sure the people
that I love are taken care of.

30:13.507 --> 30:15.814
That's all.

30:15.814 --> 30:18.207
Bumpy,
you're scaring me.

30:20.035 --> 30:21.689
I cost Mayme her job.

30:21.689 --> 30:23.647
I've been pretending
that what I do

30:23.647 --> 30:26.389
doesn't affect
the people that I love.

30:26.389 --> 30:27.869
But it does.

30:30.524 --> 30:32.004
I'm sorry.

30:34.180 --> 30:35.877
What if I stop
selling narcotics?

30:35.877 --> 30:37.661
What would that look like?

30:37.661 --> 30:39.315
Ugly.

30:39.315 --> 30:43.537
I mean, narcotics is
the backbone of your business.

30:43.537 --> 30:46.409
A wise man knows
when to change.

30:46.409 --> 30:48.194
I'm long overdue.

30:48.194 --> 30:50.370
Who's wiser than you?

30:50.370 --> 30:52.328
Malcolm.

30:52.328 --> 30:57.246
He's been trying to get me
to change my life.

30:57.246 --> 31:00.597
He's an idealist.

31:00.597 --> 31:04.079
But you--
you're a realist.

31:05.515 --> 31:09.868
Malcolm is a man who lives
to the fullest of his potential.

31:09.868 --> 31:11.347
Me...

31:11.347 --> 31:15.699
I'm just using
a fraction of mine.

31:27.015 --> 31:29.626
<i>I was told...</i>

31:29.626 --> 31:33.195
<i>you only die once,</i>

31:33.195 --> 31:37.025
<i>so you should live every day...</i>

31:37.025 --> 31:40.115
<i>to the fullest.</i>

31:40.115 --> 31:43.379
<i>♪ Yeah, will I live
to see another day? ♪</i>

31:43.379 --> 31:45.120
<i>♪ Stressed out,
heavy on my mind ♪</i>

31:45.120 --> 31:46.817
<i>♪ What my people
gotta go through ♪</i>

31:46.817 --> 31:49.037
<i>♪ Palms up, on my knees
as I pray ♪</i>

31:49.037 --> 31:50.386
<i>♪ Straighten up the bow tie</i>

31:50.386 --> 31:52.301
It's time,
Brother Minister.

31:52.301 --> 31:54.086
Yeah, I'm coming.

31:57.002 --> 31:58.786
Just a moment.

31:58.786 --> 32:01.310
<i>♪ I'm tired of singing
the flames of hatred ♪</i>

32:01.310 --> 32:03.922
<i>♪ Taking and taking
I don't care if I gotta die ♪</i>

32:03.922 --> 32:05.445
<i>♪ To make this nation</i>

32:05.445 --> 32:07.664
<i>♪ See the vision
of what we hold sacred ♪</i>

32:07.664 --> 32:09.928
<i>♪ Talk to 'em for a minute
before I meet my maker ♪</i>

32:09.928 --> 32:12.147
<i>♪ As I step up to the mic
As-Salaam Alaikum ♪</i>

32:12.147 --> 32:15.585
<i>♪ I'm just another man</i>

32:15.585 --> 32:17.500
<i>♪ Fighting through his pain</i>

32:17.500 --> 32:19.807
<i>♪ It took a lot
for what you gained ♪</i>

32:36.824 --> 32:42.134
<i>♪ Tomorrow, tomorrow</i>

32:42.134 --> 32:44.875
<i>♪ Tomorrow</i>

33:05.070 --> 33:06.854
Thank you.

33:09.509 --> 33:12.816
Well, I just heard
that you brought

33:12.816 --> 33:15.471
the education bill
to the floor.

33:15.471 --> 33:17.473
Thank you.

33:17.473 --> 33:23.523
I do feel unusually optimistic
about the country these days.

33:23.523 --> 33:25.481
The better angels of our nature
are winning,

33:25.481 --> 33:27.048
just like
Lincoln predicted.

33:27.048 --> 33:29.572
He predicted that before
they shot him in the head.

33:29.572 --> 33:30.834
Oh, you're in
a dour mood.

33:30.834 --> 33:34.316
Well, I just
can't help it.

33:34.316 --> 33:37.493
I have this sense
of foreboding.

33:37.493 --> 33:39.539
I woke up with it.

33:39.539 --> 33:41.236
I think...

33:41.236 --> 33:43.934
I think it's because
every time

33:43.934 --> 33:46.763
we make progress
in this country,

33:46.763 --> 33:50.028
something bad happens
to set us back.

33:50.028 --> 33:52.508
See, that kind of thinking
isn't like you, Adam.

33:52.508 --> 33:54.684
You've got to keep
the faith, baby.

34:31.069 --> 34:33.941
Where the fuck is Harvey?
He should be here by now.

34:48.260 --> 34:49.957
Thank you, William.

34:55.963 --> 34:57.399
Betty and the girls
are already inside.

34:57.399 --> 34:58.748
- They're in the front row.
- Right.

34:58.748 --> 35:00.402
The big question is
whether those girls

35:00.402 --> 35:02.100
can sit still
for an hour.

35:02.100 --> 35:04.667
Right this way,
Brother Minister.

35:04.667 --> 35:06.974
There's a waiting room
in the corridor to the right.

35:06.974 --> 35:08.497
Thank you.

35:12.458 --> 35:14.329
Where are Chance
and Pettigrew?

35:19.204 --> 35:21.423
Pulling up on
the Audubon Ballroom on 165th.

35:21.423 --> 35:23.164
Yeah, let's park
a few blocks away.

35:23.164 --> 35:26.689
We'll hoof it in
with the others.

35:26.689 --> 35:29.431
Let's keep an eagle eye on every
motherfucker in that room.

35:29.431 --> 35:31.433
If anybody so as squints
at Malcolm,

35:31.433 --> 35:34.262
we'll take him
the fuck out, yeah?

35:34.262 --> 35:35.742
Damn skippy.

35:42.052 --> 35:43.880
Are you kidding me?

35:43.880 --> 35:45.491
The fuck is this shit?

36:00.332 --> 36:02.551
Get out of the car.

36:02.551 --> 36:04.249
Says who?

36:06.251 --> 36:08.557
Not gonna be making it
to the Audubon today.

36:11.038 --> 36:12.561
Who the fuck are you?
NYPD?

36:12.561 --> 36:14.476
Yeah, FBI?
CIA?

36:14.476 --> 36:16.174
Take your pick.

36:16.174 --> 36:18.393
Cuff 'em.

36:18.393 --> 36:20.352
- Hey.
- Wha-- Hey!

36:21.527 --> 36:24.094
Lobby's jammed.

36:24.094 --> 36:26.314
We set 400 chairs.

36:26.314 --> 36:28.011
Looks like a lot of people
are intersected

36:28.011 --> 36:29.230
in what you have
to say.

36:29.230 --> 36:31.189
That's good news.

36:31.189 --> 36:33.582
Reverend Galamison's wife
said he was ill.

36:33.582 --> 36:34.888
He had to cancel.

36:34.888 --> 36:36.585
That's strange.

36:36.585 --> 36:39.545
Brother Carlin canceled
this afternoon.

36:39.545 --> 36:41.111
I don't think you should
go out there.

36:41.111 --> 36:43.244
It'll be fine.

36:43.244 --> 36:48.075
Why don't you go and check
on Betty and the children?

36:48.075 --> 36:50.469
Everything will be fine.

37:08.356 --> 37:10.402
If you're not
letting us frisk...

37:13.405 --> 37:15.102
then at least
do this for me.

37:15.102 --> 37:16.451
- No, brother.
- It's small, Malcolm.

37:16.451 --> 37:18.236
You can affix it to the back
of your waistband.

37:18.236 --> 37:19.759
I won't carry a gun.

37:19.759 --> 37:23.589
I cannot guarantee the safety
of this auditorium.

37:27.593 --> 37:31.640
If you won't do it for me,
do it for Betty

37:31.640 --> 37:33.163
and your children.

37:58.754 --> 38:02.280
Girls, sit up straight.

38:02.280 --> 38:04.282
When's Daddy coming on?

38:04.282 --> 38:06.849
Soon, Attallah.

38:06.849 --> 38:09.199
Hello, Elise.

38:09.199 --> 38:11.158
Ooh, look at this place.

38:11.158 --> 38:13.334
It's filling up.

38:13.334 --> 38:15.293
All kinds of new faces here.

38:15.293 --> 38:18.600
Yes.
His message is spreading.

38:41.623 --> 38:43.321
It's Chin.

38:47.107 --> 38:49.892
Fucking Bumpy Johnson.

38:49.892 --> 38:51.154
The fuck is he doing here?

38:51.154 --> 38:52.982
- I don't know.
- I knew it.

38:52.982 --> 38:55.811
These motherfuckers
are up to something.

38:55.811 --> 38:57.813
I wanna kill
these motherfuckers.

38:57.813 --> 38:59.815
Hey, hey,
slow down, slow down.

38:59.815 --> 39:04.385
Jose, put the gun down.
You hear me?

39:04.385 --> 39:07.780
You <i>hablo ingles,</i> motherfucker?
Put the goddamn gun down.

39:10.957 --> 39:12.088
Get on the fucking ground.

39:12.088 --> 39:14.482
Jose-- Jose,
put the gun down.

39:14.482 --> 39:16.179
Where the fuck
is Bill Harvey?

39:16.179 --> 39:18.225
Tell me right now or I blow
your fucking heads off.

39:18.225 --> 39:21.663
Harvey went to the Feds.
We came here to warn you.

39:21.663 --> 39:23.186
You're a fucking liar!

39:23.186 --> 39:24.492
Jose! Stop it!

39:24.492 --> 39:26.407
Put the gun down!
You cannot pop a boss!

39:26.407 --> 39:27.843
Hey, fuck you, okay?

39:27.843 --> 39:29.889
I'll fucking kill
this motherfucker then.

39:29.889 --> 39:31.499
Where the fuck is he, Bumpy?
Look at me.

39:31.499 --> 39:34.067
One chance.
Where the fuck is Harvey?

39:34.067 --> 39:36.025
William Harvey
started with the FBI.

39:36.025 --> 39:37.679
He never really left them.

39:37.679 --> 39:39.202
He's selling us out, Jose.

39:39.202 --> 39:40.595
The Feds are coming here
any minute.

39:40.595 --> 39:42.249
I'm telling you right now.

39:42.249 --> 39:43.598
Harvey's with the FBI?!

39:43.598 --> 39:45.252
That's fucking bullshit.

39:50.257 --> 39:52.215
Bumpy, I told you
never fuck with me!

39:58.787 --> 40:01.224
- Get down! Hands up!
- Take 'em down.

40:07.274 --> 40:09.145
Alright, alright,
alright, alright.

40:09.145 --> 40:10.756
Okay, okay, okay, okay.

40:34.475 --> 40:35.563
Betty and the girls
are good?

40:35.563 --> 40:37.652
Yes.

40:37.652 --> 40:40.089
But there are some men out there
who give me the chills.

40:40.089 --> 40:41.874
I'm gonna go
out there.

40:44.311 --> 40:46.139
Best wishes,
Brother Minister.

40:46.139 --> 40:47.836
Thank you, Omar.

40:57.455 --> 41:00.849
I can't thank you enough for
everything you've done for me.

41:00.849 --> 41:02.503
And for our cause.

41:02.503 --> 41:04.462
We have a lot more to do.

41:04.462 --> 41:06.942
Yes, we do.

41:06.942 --> 41:08.509
Both of us.

41:11.817 --> 41:13.645
It's time.

41:13.645 --> 41:16.299
Brother Benjamin's making
the introductory remarks.

41:16.299 --> 41:17.910
Thank you.

41:20.260 --> 41:21.870
Malcolm, wait.

41:55.513 --> 41:57.384
Brothers and sisters,

41:57.384 --> 41:59.560
I will now introduce to you

41:59.560 --> 42:03.521
a man who would give his life
for his people.

42:35.727 --> 42:40.558
- As-Salaam Alaikum.
- Wa Alaikum Salaam.

43:02.449 --> 43:04.799
Hey, get your hand
out of my pocket!

43:04.799 --> 43:06.496
Hold-- Hold it, brother...

43:06.496 --> 43:07.889
Hold it! Hold it!

44:23.748 --> 44:26.054
They're killing my husband!

44:39.589 --> 44:41.548
No!

44:44.420 --> 44:46.292
No! No!

45:06.529 --> 45:10.490
He's gone.
He's gone.

45:12.666 --> 45:16.061
He's gone!
He's gone.

45:17.497 --> 45:22.415
Betty-- Betty, I have to take
the weapon away from him now.

45:22.415 --> 45:24.634
If the cops find it,
they'll say it was just

45:24.634 --> 45:28.377
two niggers in a gun fight
and they won't investigate.

45:33.600 --> 45:36.298
Betty, I'm-- I'm sorry.

45:39.649 --> 45:46.221
Why? Why?!

45:51.270 --> 45:56.057
Oh, Malcolm.
Oh, Malcolm.

46:18.993 --> 46:20.952
Ah.

46:23.650 --> 46:27.306
It was my understanding
that you'd lead me to Harvey.

46:27.306 --> 46:29.438
Instead, I got handed
a 50-inch belt

46:29.438 --> 46:32.659
and a pair of Florsheims
from the coroner.

46:32.659 --> 46:35.531
I heard he got drunk
on a roof and fell off.

46:35.531 --> 46:37.490
Yeah, he loves
his Cutty Sark.

46:37.490 --> 46:39.492
It affected his balance.

46:39.492 --> 46:41.102
Hmm.

46:41.102 --> 46:44.845
Well, that's cute.
Very cute.

46:44.845 --> 46:47.848
Which one's Abbott
and which one's Costello?

46:47.848 --> 46:49.545
Hmm?

46:49.545 --> 46:52.157
You expect me to believe
this shit when you say it?

46:52.157 --> 46:54.507
Aside from the shipment
you just seized,

46:54.507 --> 46:57.640
we helped you stop
an illegal CIA plot.

46:57.640 --> 47:01.035
If it goes public,
there'll be a shitstorm.

47:12.351 --> 47:14.353
Don't worry, boys.

47:14.353 --> 47:17.573
I'm keeping my end
of the bargain.

47:17.573 --> 47:20.315
But I promise you this.

47:20.315 --> 47:22.491
Next time I see you,

47:22.491 --> 47:25.712
you'll be doing your little
comedy routine from Rikers.

47:28.541 --> 47:31.849
Alright, uncuff them.
Let 'em go.

47:33.938 --> 47:36.723
Did you see
the look on Colombo's face

47:36.723 --> 47:38.333
when the Feds rolled up?

47:38.333 --> 47:42.337
That was fucking priceless,
let me tell you.

47:42.337 --> 47:44.339
You and I,
we own this town.

47:44.339 --> 47:45.775
Harlem's ours.

47:45.775 --> 47:47.603
I got what I wanted.

47:47.603 --> 47:50.084
That motherfucker
Harvey is dead,

47:50.084 --> 47:51.694
and Battle and Colombo,

47:51.694 --> 47:53.783
they won't be coming
after me or my family.

47:56.438 --> 48:00.181
I'm getting out
of narcotics.

48:00.181 --> 48:02.227
What are you
talking about?

48:02.227 --> 48:03.924
I'm making a change.

48:03.924 --> 48:05.230
What do you mean?

48:09.147 --> 48:12.106
Harlem is yours.

48:12.106 --> 48:13.803
<i>We interrupt this program</i>

48:13.803 --> 48:15.544
<i>for an important bulletin.</i>

48:15.544 --> 48:17.807
<i>A shooting has occurred
in Harlem's Audubon Ballroom.</i>

48:17.807 --> 48:19.461
<i>While giving a speech
to his followers,</i>

48:19.461 --> 48:22.290
<i>Malcolm X was shot dead
by unknown assailants...</i>

48:24.989 --> 48:26.425
<i>He said, "Stay cool,"
"Stay calm,"</i>

48:26.425 --> 48:29.036
<i>or something like that,
and, uh, just then,</i>

48:29.036 --> 48:31.082
<i>the gunfire went off,
and his-- his hand was up.</i>

48:31.082 --> 48:33.040
<i>I remember this.
I turned around quickly,</i>

48:33.040 --> 48:34.433
<i>and the next thing I saw was--</i>

48:34.433 --> 48:37.653
<i>was Malcolm falling back
in a dead faint.</i>

48:37.653 --> 48:40.743
<i>Um, right after that,
of course, like everybody else,</i>

48:40.743 --> 48:42.441
<i>you know, chairs
were being knocked over,</i>

48:42.441 --> 48:45.444
<i>there were screams, uh,
everybody was in a mad...</i>

48:45.444 --> 48:48.142
I-I need to go home now.

48:48.142 --> 48:49.927
I understand.

48:52.799 --> 48:55.497
My people need me.

48:55.497 --> 48:57.543
Your Nation needs you.

48:59.806 --> 49:01.939
J. Edgar Hoover
has informed me

49:01.939 --> 49:05.855
that suspects from a mosque
in New Jersey were responsible.

49:05.855 --> 49:07.074
Hoover said that?

49:07.074 --> 49:09.424
Well, then
it must be true.

49:09.424 --> 49:13.037
We need
to preach calm now, Adam.

49:14.081 --> 49:17.084
He was the brightest
and the best of us,

49:17.084 --> 49:20.174
so they shot him down.

49:20.174 --> 49:23.351
Didn't anybody
hear anything?

49:23.351 --> 49:26.311
How about the FBI?

49:26.311 --> 49:29.270
Hoover said they were taken
completely by surprise.

49:29.270 --> 49:31.316
Oh, now you know
that is bullshit.

49:33.492 --> 49:35.711
The truth will come out.

49:35.711 --> 49:39.324
Besides, we can't
bring him back.

49:42.849 --> 49:49.029
You can kill a man, Adam,
but not his ideas.

49:49.029 --> 49:51.162
They will live on.

49:51.162 --> 49:52.859
You'll see.

50:21.018 --> 50:23.585
I did what you said, Malcolm.

50:26.588 --> 50:28.460
Tried to do the right thing.

50:30.810 --> 50:32.638
That's what you wanted, right?

50:36.076 --> 50:39.079
Stubborn fool!

50:39.079 --> 50:42.735
Who's laying on the slab now,
you or me?

50:45.825 --> 50:48.567
I tried to protect you.

50:48.567 --> 50:50.569
Why wouldn't you let me?

50:52.919 --> 50:57.054
How am I supposed
to forgive myself for this?

51:09.936 --> 51:13.592
I promise you, Malcolm...

51:13.592 --> 51:17.683
one day, I'm gonna be the man
that you wanted me to be.

51:19.859 --> 51:25.473
May we all-- our people--
be who you wanted us to be.

51:28.607 --> 51:31.262
But this is hard to swallow.

51:35.483 --> 51:40.445
It's got its hand on my throat,
and it's--

51:40.445 --> 51:42.534
it's yanking me back in.

51:45.885 --> 51:49.671
So, I promise you
this, as well.

51:52.196 --> 51:56.330
Whatever forces put you here,

51:56.330 --> 51:59.507
I will have vengeance.
